Self-hosted web fonts for gakudan_liveboard.

These WOFF2 files are bundled so the dashboard makes no off-origin requests
(GDPR by design). They are fetched by scripts/fetch-fonts.sh. Both families are
licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1 (OFL), which permits bundling and
redistribution:

- IBM Plex Mono   - (c) IBM Corp.            - https://github.com/IBM/plex
- Instrument Serif- (c) Rosetta Type / Instrument - https://github.com/Instrument/instrument-serif

SIL OFL 1.1: https://openfontlicense.org/

Latin subset only; regenerate with `make fonts` (scripts/fetch-fonts.sh).
